    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A rogue-lite where instead of battling monsters, you battle trivia questions! On your way to the top you have the chance of discovering various events and artifacts, which may help or hinder your progress. Every time you die you gain XP and level up, which unlocks additional skills to help you on your climb to the top. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FEATURES: <br>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated trees of trivia. Every climb will be different </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113600/extras/67f8fa4fdd56e0d89ab16bada81cb41d.avif?t=1769012527\" width=942 height=1345 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 4 000 different quiz questions divided into over a hundred different categories</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113600/extras/a279ad81ff2e5a95f032cfb10bfdf83f.poster.avif?t=1769012527\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113600/extras/a279ad81ff2e5a95f032cfb10bfdf83f.webm?t=1769012527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113600/extras/a279ad81ff2e5a95f032cfb10bfdf83f.mp4?t=1769012527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain powerful artifacts which impacts your game and makes every climb different</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113600/extras/b36cab643155680560ef05ca55865d94.poster.avif?t=1769012527\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113600/extras/b36cab643155680560ef05ca55865d94.webm?t=1769012527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113600/extras/b36cab643155680560ef05ca55865d94.mp4?t=1769012527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plenty of meta progression in the form of skills, quests and rewards</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113600/extras/0d238e491f8df144dbdbc1ccc9d5b15e.poster.avif?t=1769012527\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113600/extras/0d238e491f8df144dbdbc1ccc9d5b15e.webm?t=1769012527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113600/extras/0d238e491f8df144dbdbc1ccc9d5b15e.mp4?t=1769012527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See you at the top!</p>",
